infoTags.title: Aerath
infoTags.description: The name of the planet, a world teeming with magic, diverse races, and ancient history.

infoTags.title: Beastkin
infoTags.description: A diverse group of races possessing both humanoid and animalistic features. They are one of the most populous races on Aerath.

infoTags.title: Noble Class
infoTags.description: The ruling class of society. Nobles typically possess powerful magic inherited through their lineage and hold significant political and social power.

infoTags.title: Commoner Class
infoTags.description: The majority of the population. Commoners have varying degrees of magical ability, but are generally considered weaker and of lower social standing than Nobles.

infoTags.title: Altheim Academy for the Arcane and Martial
infoTags.description: The most renowned magical academy on Aerath, where students from all walks of life come to train as mages, warriors, and supports.
